productReviews.reviewText: My co-worker Skylar has one of these. He says it looks sweaty.
It only works when I'm Guernsey.
i use it until further notice when i'm in my nightclub.
I tried to electrocute it but got sweetmeat all over it.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This synthesizing keeps them away.
